  <trk>
    <name>Gibidumpass</name>
    <desc>This high path runs along the tree line from Visperterminen to Gspon, passing old larch forests and a rich alpine flora. On the 11-kilometre hike, you have a breathtaking view of the Visp valley.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
